<heading>stop - Cancel a running flow.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  stop index
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Cancels a running flow identified by its job index.

Use the list command to see active flows and their indices.
Once stopped, the flow cannot be resumed.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
list, bg, fg, man
</paragraph>
